==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Unexampled
<hw>Un`ex*am"pled</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having no
example or similar case; being without precedent; unprecedented;
unparalleled.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧A revolution . . . <xex>unexampled</xex> for
grandeur of results.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>De Quincey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unexceptionable</ent>⟦br⟧
